---
import Icon from "./Icon.astro";
import Typography from "./Typography.astro";
import Leaf from "./icons/Leaf.astro";
---

<div class="flex flex-col pb-20 pt-10" aria-label="cuenta atrás">
  <Typography
    as="h3"
    color="black"
    class:list={"text-balance text-center tracking-widest text-[50px]"}
    >Itinerario
  </Typography>
  <Icon>
    <Leaf class="w-7 h-7 fill-primary" />
  </Icon>
  <div class="mt-4 p-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col grid-cols-9 p-2 mx-auto md:grid">
      <div class="flex md:contents flex-row-reverse">
        <div
          class="relative p-4 my-2 max-w-lg text-primary rounded-xl col-start-1 col-end-5 mr-auto md:mr-0 md:ml-auto"
        >
          <h3 class="text-2xl my-6 lg:text-4xl font-light tracking-widest">
            Ceremonia Religiosa
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 my-6 leading-6 font-extralight tracking-widest">
            5:00 pm
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 my-6 leading-6 font-extralight tracking-widest">
            La misa se llevará a cabo en la Parroquia San Pablo, Las Fuentes.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative col-start-5 col-end-6 mr-7 md:mx-auto">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-full">
            <div class="w-[2px] h-full bg-primary rounded-t-full"></div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute w-6 h-6 -mt-3 bg-white border-2 border-primary rounded-full top-1/2"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex md:contents">
        <div class="relative col-start-5 col-end-6 mr-7 md:mx-auto">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-full">
            <div class="w-[2px] h-full bg-primary"></div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute w-6 h-6 -mt-3 bg-white border-2 border-primary rounded-full top-1/2"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="relative p-4 my-2 max-w-lg text-primary rounded-xl col-start-6 col-end-10 mr-auto"
        >
          <h3 class="text-2xl my-6 lg:text-4xl font-light tracking-widest">
            Cóctel
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 my-6 leading-6 font-extralight tracking-widest">
            6:30 pm
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 my-6 leading-6 font-extralight tracking-widest">
            Los esperamos Akacia Terraza, con unos buenos drinks para dar inicio
            al festejo!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex md:contents flex-row-reverse">
        <div
          class="relative p-4 my-2 max-w-lg text-primary rounded-xl col-start-1 col-end-5 mr-auto md:mr-0 md:ml-auto"
        >
          <h3 class="text-2xl my-6 lg:text-4xl font-light tracking-widest">
            Ceremonia Civil
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 my-6 leading-6 font-extralight tracking-widest">
            7:00 pm
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative col-start-5 col-end-6 mr-7 md:mx-auto">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-full">
            <div class="w-[2px] h-full bg-primary rounded-t-full"></div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute w-6 h-6 -mt-3 bg-white border-2 border-primary rounded-full top-1/2"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex md:contents">
        <div class="relative col-start-5 col-end-6 mr-7 md:mx-auto">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-full">
            <div class="w-[2px] h-full bg-primary"></div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute w-6 h-6 -mt-3 bg-white border-2 border-primary rounded-full top-1/2"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="relative p-4 my-2 max-w-lg text-primary rounded-xl col-start-6 col-end-10 mr-auto"
        >
          <h3 class="text-2xl my-6 lg:text-4xl font-light tracking-widest">
            ¡Que Inicie la Fiesta!
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 my-6 leading-6 font-extralight tracking-widest">
            7:30 pm
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 my-6 leading-6 font-extralight tracking-widest">
            ¡La celebración está por comenzar! Prepárense para disfrutar de una
            noche inolvidable llena de música, baile y momentos memorables.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex md:contents flex-row-reverse">
        <div
          class="relative p-4 my-2 max-w-lg text-primary rounded-xl col-start-1 col-end-5 mr-auto md:mr-0 md:ml-auto"
        >
          <h3 class="text-2xl my-6 lg:text-4xl font-light tracking-widest">
            Fin del Evento
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 my-6 leading-6 font-extralight tracking-widest">
            2:30 am
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 my-6 leading-6 font-extralight tracking-widest">
            Ha sido una noche maravillosa y esperamos que cada uno de ustedes la
            haya disfrutado al máximo. Es momento de descansar, y queremos
            agradecerles por ser parte de este día tan especial en nuestras
            vidas.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative col-start-5 col-end-6 mr-7 md:mx-auto">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-full">
            <div class="w-[2px] h-full bg-primary rounded-t-full"></div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute w-6 h-6 -mt-3 bg-white border-2 border-primary rounded-full top-1/2"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
